Tanıtılan Reduce energy costs while boosting shredder performance! With Lindemann’s Variable Frequency Drive (VFD) and Shredder Drive Assistant (SDA), you can achieve up to 20% energy savings while significantly increasing throughput and efficiency.

Traditional shredder drives suffer from sudden load peaks and high energy consumption due to fluctuating material feeds. Our VFD technology dynamically adjusts speed and torque to match real-time demand, eliminating unnecessary power spikes and ensuring smooth operation.

Tanıtılan Thévenaz-Leduc, Europe's pioneering metal recycler, achieved rapid ROI by upgrading their shredder with Lindemann’s Shredder Drive Assistant.

Standard shredder operations leave efficiency gains untapped and expose recyclers to costly energy peaks that inflate quarterly bills.

Lindemann’s SDA technology optimizes feeding for consistent throughput while eliminating expensive power spikes - even with challenging materials.

“In this era of high-energy bills, we are never satisfied unless operating at maximum efficiency!" - Blesi Roger, Managing Director Thévenaz-Leduc.
